@startuml sequence-error-payment
title Ошибка: Превышение лимита категории (Error Case)
skinparam maxMessageSize 150

actor "Член семьи" as User
participant "WebApp UI" as UI
participant "Budget API" as API
participant "Database" as DB

User -> UI: Ввод суммы (очень большой)
activate UI

UI -> API: POST /api/expenses\n(amount=50000)
activate API

API -> DB: SELECT limit, spent FROM categories
activate DB
DB --> API: limit=20000, spent=15000
deactivate DB

note right of API
  Проверка: 15000 + 50000 > 20000
  Лимит превышен!
end note

API --> UI: 400 Bad Request\n{"error": "Limit_Exceeded"}
deactivate API

UI --> User: "Ошибка: Превышен лимит по категории!"
deactivate UI
@enduml